];

Solution 1Our first thought was like this:
type First&lt;T extends any[]&gt; = T[0];

This will solve most of test cases, but failed when T is an empty array. So we can add a conditional return:
type First&lt;T extends any[]&gt; = T extends [] ? never : T[0];

Solution 2Instead of checking T extends [], we can check its length type. From previous tests we know there‚Äôs a length property on array&#x2F;tuple type, so we can do:
