Solution 3We can also check if T[0] is in array:
type First&lt;T extends any[]&gt; = T[0] extends T[number] ? T[0] : never;

Solution 4We can also use infer to get the type of the first element of the array:
type First&lt;T extends any[]&gt; = T extends [infer FIRST, ...infer REST]
  ? FIRST
  : never;

