Let‚Äôs get started!
00268 Easy IfImplement a util If which accepts condition C, a truthy return type T, and a falsy return type F. C is expected to be either true or false while T and F can be any type.
For example:
type A = If&lt;true, &quot;a&quot;, &quot;b&quot;&gt;; // expected to be &#39;a&#39;
